{"tid":3934,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"白手興家3年 你問我答","createTime":"2016-11-26T10:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T11:40:25.000Z","uid":9760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f5610ff5cf245e0b77c548044920a92213064d","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:33:45.000Z","msg":"唔係R 生意，所以唔會點講公司做咩產品<br />\n純粹幫LIHKG 開多個post 希望帶到d 人氣<br />\n<br />\n背景： 公屋仔 無家底 而家應該算守緊業<br />\n識得我既人 麻煩高抬貴手 唔好起底"},{"pid":"d7a6e21c529c6619ae6a75ed54b7ab9c99f725f7","tid":3934,"uid":10941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"唔講邊類生意好難問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開始晚資金點黎？"},{"pid":"43351b970f3879c9482f2d3a088c6aa5e3bd004e","tid":3934,"uid":10941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔講邊類生意好難問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開始<span style=\"color: red;\">既</span>資金點黎？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b8a1ecbcb4a9f2109fb6bd7271d328f71e806bbd","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔講邊類生意好難問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開始<span style=\"color: red;\">既</span>資金點黎？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行業偏向IT, 都幾專既行業黎<br />\n<br />\n資金係打左三年工， 個陣應該儲左1x 萬"},{"pid":"098e12c80a6ce9b421029747cfdfcc56d08b02fd","tid":3934,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"咩因素令你有信心去創業"},{"pid":"03703160c89e3b629786b07fc5288e7671fc6040","tid":3934,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"食左飯未"},{"pid":"834e35e87006db566b020f740c31ef1c89d6195c","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩因素令你有信心去創業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都無諗過創業 <br />\n個陣唔係因為有信心 應該係硬頸<br />\n舊公司做極都得唔到信任 只有人工<br />\n之後轉行 發覺新公司同我想像唔同 亦都唔鍾意<br />\n所以好快辭職 個陣覺得應該好易既 10萬咩都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd1aa171de0bfc4da27c41e38539d8457b8d580","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左飯未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩落車行緊去hostel <br />\n放低野就出去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682d20d1d058630d5dfdd7ea2a798223b6e0f2e1","tid":3934,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩因素令你有信心去創業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都無諗過創業 <br />\n個陣唔係因為有信心 應該係硬頸<br />\n舊公司做極都得唔到信任 只有人工<br />\n之後轉行 發覺新公司同我想像唔同 亦都唔鍾意<br />\n所以好快辭職 個陣覺得應該好易既 10萬咩都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到真喺好易咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c58201bab5a402355d6947d0e5075de26341f1","tid":3934,"uid":19333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"請人嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6852f5eb2a702e3913660431188ab2178b08de3a","tid":3934,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"公司發展需要人才<br />\n不如講下未來需要咩人"},{"pid":"f272cf073d8c995101fc43bf93c6afc3d3ba5dcd","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩因素令你有信心去創業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都無諗過創業 <br />\n個陣唔係因為有信心 應該係硬頸<br />\n舊公司做極都得唔到信任 只有人工<br />\n之後轉行 發覺新公司同我想像唔同 亦都唔鍾意<br />\n所以好快辭職 個陣覺得應該好易既 10萬咩都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到真喺好易咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣自己幻想真係好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起左步先知中招 <br />\n不過如果一早知中招 之後無去做<br />\n而家應該變左浮浮沉沉既奴工"},{"pid":"0b3b9a0d37e1840acbe2baf45a7765b4a2d03612","tid":3934,"uid":19406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"而家搵幾錢？"},{"pid":"085b2a2d37ab88541681cd065f97022e5025c110","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請人嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有諗緊<br />\n不過呢個post 唔係請人"},{"pid":"ece92083ff1f5117c09ad4ddff6ceb02a94e5e1e","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司發展需要人才<br />\n不如講下未來需要咩人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得人分對內同對外<br />\n<br />\n對外即係sales<br />\n對內即係跟單 倉 account 之類<br />\n<br />\n對內暫時ok 請到個好盡責 如果生意再多會請多個人幫佢手<br />\n<br />\n對外 其實把口要好 學歷唔洗高 最緊要係有心 要諗幫客解決問題 唔係諗點賺佢錢"},{"pid":"2cadb890bf5746571f5caab31d09e5b084429449","tid":3934,"uid":22952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩因素令你有信心去創業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由細到大都無諗過創業 <br />\n個陣唔係因為有信心 應該係硬頸<br />\n舊公司做極都得唔到信任 只有人工<br />\n之後轉行 發覺新公司同我想像唔同 亦都唔鍾意<br />\n所以好快辭職 個陣覺得應該好易既 10萬咩都夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講到真喺好易咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣自己幻想真係好易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起左步先知中招 <br />\n不過如果一早知中招 之後無去做<br />\n而家應該變左浮浮沉沉既奴工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2465f4358663ca965c7ee048e912b8411f5eae69","tid":3934,"uid":9760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家搵幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個月起起趺趺<br />\n自己本身創業唔係諗發達<br />\n所以搵錢唔多 夠比每個月11k 家用同自己洗費<br />\n<br />\n有限公司關係 我都係當出糧 每個月固定數<br />\n<br />\n公司有錢多唔會私下拎 等年尾出雙糧+bonus 用<br />\n得我無份出雙糧+bonus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再有多就做應急同睇下會唔會入多d 貨"},{"pid":"e7092c53dc5248916f15849ec1ab950fa82af2d6","tid":3934,"uid":12902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"而家公司有幾多人？？"}]}